snippet.title: Kantara Chapter 1 Trailer - Telugu | Rishab Shetty | Rukmini | Vijay Kiragandur | Hombale Films
snippet.description:
From Hombale Films ‚Äî the makers behind KGF: Chapter 1 & 2 and Salaar ‚Äî and the visionary, National Award‚Äìwinning Filmmaker and Actor Rishab Shetty, comes the official trailer for Kantara: A Legend ‚Äì Chapter 1. 

Starring Rishab Shetty as Berme, Rukmini Vasanth as Kanakavathi, and Gulshan Devaiah as Kulashekara, supported by a formidable ensemble cast.With a soul-stirring score by B. Ajaneesh Loknath and produced by Vijay Kiragandur under Hombale Films, Kantara: A Legend ‚Äì Chapter 1 promises visceral action, haunting melodies and a saga that will echo through generations. 

Witness India's Divine Epic on Screens this 2 October 2025.

snippet.title: I Went to FFMIC and Total Gaming Became CS Champion üèÜüî• Live Reaction üò≥
snippet.description:
Today, I witnessed one of the best comebacks in Free Fire history! After four years, the Free Fire India Max Cup returned, and Total Gaming pulled off an epic BOOYAH! In the finals against GodL, GodL had a 2-point lead in the best-of-five series. But Total Gaming made an incredible comeback, leveling the score 2-2. In the final match, with the score tied 5-5, Total Gaming clinched the victory in the last round. It was truly an epic comeback and one of the greatest moments in Free Fire‚Äôs history!

A big shoutout and congratulations to Ajju Bhai, Total Gaming, Fauji ajay mafia and Delete & all for their outstanding performance! Also, kudos to Jonty Gaming and NG Pros for their amazing gameplay. And let‚Äôs not forget Marco from the GodL team, whose sniping was absolutely top notch!

All the best to everyone in the battle royale matches today

On the eighth day of Navratri, devotees worship Maa Mahagauri, the symbol of purity, serenity, and divine beauty. Chanting the Mahagauri Mantra blesses devotees with peace, prosperity, and the removal of all past sins. üôè
